summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2482 for the improvement of Twenty-third Avenue West and Twenty-third Avenue West Produced, from the intersection of West Garfield Street to West Newton Street, all in The City of Seattle, by constructing a bridge roadway thereon Twenty-six (26) feet in width, and by doing such grading as may be necessary, under Ordinance No. 26851, and levying and assessing the amount thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
